query:
/*+ NoNestLoop(cd ss p) NoNestLoop(cd p ss dd) NoMergeJoin(cd dd p ss i) */ select i.i_item_id,
avg(ss.ss_quantity) AS agg1,
avg(ss.ss_list_price) AS agg2,
avg(ss.ss_coupon_amt) AS agg3,
avg(ss.ss_sales_price) AS agg4
from customer_demographics AS cd
inner join store_sales AS ss
on ss.ss_cdemo_sk = cd.cd_demo_sk AND cd.cd_gender = 'F' AND cd.cd_marital_status = 'W' AND cd.cd_education_status = 'Primary'
inner join promotion AS p
on ss.ss_promo_sk = p.p_promo_sk AND ( p.p_channel_email = 'N' OR p.p_channel_event = 'N')
inner join date_dim AS dd
on ss.ss_sold_date_sk = dd.d_date_sk AND dd.d_year = 1998
inner join item AS i
on ss.ss_item_sk = i.i_item_sk group by i.i_item_id order by i.i_item_id LIMIT 100;
